<dl id="n12158b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12158b">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12158b"> 158(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Sabian idolatry </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Little is known about the Sabians, a religious sect referred to three times in the Koran (ii. 40, v. 73, xxii, 17), and by later Arab writers, some of whom claim that they secretly worshipped the stars. </mm> </dd></dl>
